<h1 class="mt-5">Fediverse* Explorer <sup><span class="badge rounded-pill text-bg-info">Beta</span></sup></h1>
<p class="lead">Browse most recent public posts across the fediverse.</p>
<p>This tool is a prototype and under active development. *Currently only supports Mastodon instances. No data is saved on this server.</p>
<form id="tag-browser">
    <div class="input-group mb-3">
        <div class="form-floating">
            <input id="tag" type="text" class="form-control" name="tag" placeholder="music" value="introduction">
            <label for="tag">Tag</label>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="submit" id="browse">Browse</button>
    </div>
    <div class="form-floating">
        <textarea id="instances" class="form-control" style="min-height: 8rem;" rows="14" placeholder="mastodon.social,pawoo.net,mstdn.jp,mastodon.cloud,mstdn.social,mas.to,mastodon.art,techhub.social,mastodon.lol,fosstodon.org,vis.social">mastodon.social
pawoo.net
mstdn.jp
mastodon.cloud
mstdn.social
mas.to
mastodon.art
techhub.social
mastodon.lol
fosstodon.org
vis.social</textarea>
        <label for="floatingTextarea">Instances</label>
        <button id="reset-instance-list" class="btn btn-link">Reset</button>
    </div>
</form>
<div id="results" class="container mt-4 mb-4 g-0">
</div>                
